code: @Override protected NodeInfo<Or> info() {     return NodeInfo.create(this, Or::new, left(), right()). }
@Override protected Or replaceChildren(Expression newLeft, Expression newRight) {     return new Or(source(), newLeft, newRight). }
@Override public Or swapLeftAndRight() {     return new Or(source(), right(), left()). }
@Override public And negate() {     return new And(source(), new Not(source(), left()), new Not(source(), right())). }
